title: Satanic Warmaster - Strength and Honour 2001 [remastered 2007]
description:
First album of Finnish one-man black metal band Satanic Warmaster. Originally, its released in 2001 by Northern Heritage. This is 2007 reissue with remastered sound and bonus tracks (Blutrache's 1999 demo - Marsch Zu Neuen Zeitaltern)

Strength and Honour 2001:
1. Raging Winter
2. A New Black Order
3. The Burning Eyes of the Werewolf
4. Strength and Honour
5. Wolves of Blood and Iron
6. Der Schwarze Orden
7. Night of Retribution
8. Legion Werewolf
Blutrache - Marsch Zu Neuen Zeitaltern (Demo) 1999:
9. Ewiges Zwielicht (Intro)
10. Eternal War
11. Marching Towards The New Aeon
12. Die Rache Das Heidenbluts
13. Arische Freiheit (Outro)

Cat. # NH-016B
